# SclJet SQL WHERE set/range predicates (BETWEEN, IN, NOT IN)

`WHERE` predicates beyond scalar comparisons: `col BETWEEN lo AND hi` (inclusive range, the inner
`AND` belongs to BETWEEN — a following `AND` still chains normally), `col IN (v1, v2, …)` and
`col NOT IN (…)` (membership over a literal list; text or integer). Each is a single predicate, so it
composes with `AND`/`OR` and `ORDER BY`. Every result is byte-identical to reference sqlite3 running
the same SQL on the same file (verified out-of-band); locked here across backends.

[ByteSlice, SqliteValue, SqlInteger, SqlText, buildTableDatabase](std/scljet/index.ssc)
[queryImage, renderRows](std/scljet/sql.ssc)

```scalascript
def show(db: ByteSlice, sql: String): Unit =
  queryImage(db, sql) match
    case Left(m) => println(sql + " => ERR:" + m)
    case Right(rows) => println(sql + " => " + renderRows(rows).toString)

buildTableDatabase(512, 1, 1, "emp", "CREATE TABLE emp(id INTEGER, name TEXT, dept INTEGER, salary INTEGER)",
  List(List(SqlInteger(1L), SqlText("ann"), SqlInteger(10L), SqlInteger(100L)),
       List(SqlInteger(2L), SqlText("bob"), SqlInteger(20L), SqlInteger(250L)),
       List(SqlInteger(3L), SqlText("cat"), SqlInteger(10L), SqlInteger(300L)),
       List(SqlInteger(4L), SqlText("dan"), SqlInteger(30L), SqlInteger(150L)),
       List(SqlInteger(5L), SqlText("eve"), SqlInteger(20L), SqlInteger(250L)),
       List(SqlInteger(6L), SqlText("flo"), SqlInteger(10L), SqlInteger(120L)))) match
  case Left(error) => println("build-error:" + error.message)
  case Right(db) =>
    show(db, "SELECT id FROM emp WHERE salary BETWEEN 120 AND 250")
    show(db, "SELECT name FROM emp WHERE dept IN (10, 30)")
    show(db, "SELECT id FROM emp WHERE dept NOT IN (10, 20)")
    show(db, "SELECT name FROM emp WHERE name IN ('ann', 'flo', 'zzz')")
    show(db, "SELECT id FROM emp WHERE salary BETWEEN 120 AND 250 AND dept = 10")
    show(db, "SELECT id, salary FROM emp WHERE dept IN (10, 20) AND salary > 120 ORDER BY id")
    show(db, "SELECT COUNT(*) FROM emp WHERE dept NOT IN (20)")
```
